values:
&nbsp;i'm at work. and i'm super bored.

ron and i are going on "holiday" the end of october. i'm stoked.&nbsp;

i'm also stoked that it's jacket weather. and the air smells different. fall rules.&nbsp;

last night ron and i went to the city and bought lots of new cds. i love shopping for music with him. i always start at a, and he starts at z and we work our way toward each other. knowing how to not get in your way is an awesome quality for a dude to possess. kidding.&nbsp;

i started to take down the wallpaper in our upstairs bathroom. i forgot what a pain in the ass this process is. ugh, it's going to take forever. it'll be worth it when i'm done though, that wallpaper was so fucking disgusting. i haven't decided on what color i'm going to paint it yet, i'm leaning toward a pale blue or yellow. we'll see.&nbsp;

ok, now things are happening.

my name is sycamore.

wow, the last time i said something in this thing was back in may.&nbsp;

summer's not so bad. today is beautiful and i'm stuck in work. i want to play. i should be getting done early, though. 

tonight should be fun&nbsp;at pat's house. shenanigans. i think i'll make cupcakes.&nbsp;

byeee.
